## Test Database

### Setup

```bash
# Create test database
rails db:test:prepare

# Reset test database
rails db:test:purge
rails db:test:prepare

# Load schema to test database
rails db:schema:load RAILS_ENV=test
```

### Database Cleaner

```ruby
# Test database is automatically cleaned between tests
# Rails uses transactional fixtures by default

# In test_helper.rb
class ActiveSupport::TestCase
  # Use transactional fixtures
  self.use_transactional_tests = true
end
```

